{"tid":1829490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"斥英國領事館縱港警危害使館範圍集會者 市民轟主動棄保衞領土責任","createTime":"2020-01-18T18:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T05:58:57.000Z","uid":92301,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6073324e78f9303482968d3fd9ec1eed8c3733e","tid":1829490,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"上周六（11日）有網民響應「全民連儂日」，到英國總領事館一帶展示文宣，但多名防暴警突於領事館外驅逐在場人士，並拘捕一名15歲少女，指控她涉嫌在領事館一帶的馬路石壆塗鴉，惹來外界質疑警方越界執法。但英國外交及聯邦事務部後來承認，當日是英領館主動聯絡警方，報稱館外有潛在犯罪行為，又指涉案地點為公眾地方，屬於香港政府租借予英國的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n主張港獨、重回英聯邦的「香港獨立黨」代表方先生今晚在領事館前見傳媒，批評英領報警做法極之荒謬，斥英領職員任由警察威嚇和危害使館範圍內的和平集會人士，是對警暴問題視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n他指，曾有示威者於2014年進入英領外灰色階磚範圍，但當時保安以「英國領土」為由，要求在場人士離開，但英國外交及聯邦事務部卻推翻過往講法。他批評，英國主動放棄保衞英國領土的責任，事件再次證實《中英聯合聲明》承諾淪為泡影。<br />\n<br />\n獨立黨要求，英國外交事務部承認錯失，並作出實際行動，包括承諾協助被捕女童等集會人士、澄清大使館內的英國領土範圍，和處置失職員工。<br />\n<br />\n目擊當日事發經過的施女士指，有市民在英國領事館對出馬路貼文宣，得知有防暴警察突襲，誤以為走入英領範圍會安全。現場人士曾向英領保安員求助，但無人理會，防暴警察逐一向現場人士搜身和檢查證件，但拒絕解釋原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200118/HPILQIT4PWYZTLQWD6LFRML4IY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200118%2FHPILQIT4PWYZTLQWD6LFRML4IY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1DizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=97e5edc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200118%2FHPILQIT4PWYZTLQWD6LFRML4IY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=7684cbd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200118/HPILQIT4PWYZTLQWD6LFRML4IY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"4a60ce98eefe079798a194266a68a7985f30d070","tid":1829490,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T18:41:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d89b89b6a2aa5b7712e66d5ac608c4955a20a964","tid":1829490,"uid":226413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"沒有普選，唯有獨立"},{"pid":"91e624e3c3c6632fbbb725b7c3443e89657e3863","tid":1829490,"uid":320135,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:25:26.000Z","msg":"仲有人想歸英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班白皮豬奶共奶到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dc10a7e96667b25aa2fc1da05db774584da4b3","tid":1829490,"uid":76148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T20:07:11.000Z","msg":"廢國含撚"},{"pid":"2013affc908f8645d0818b011a314c3fe94ea76f","tid":1829490,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df981f937ac0c8678d8807d830906b2e584a4d83","tid":1829490,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"No glory, No guts, only sunset"},{"pid":"1b63bc18e215dcf47301299a2bfdf766c1511d44","tid":1829490,"uid":253691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"準時 2 點遮打見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n❮警世，不戀戰❯ 戰略目標，達成就散<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1829804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1829804</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}